{"tid":191111,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我有兩份工，你會點揀","createTime":"2017-04-07T15:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T02:19:24.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"285451ac39b9389cc0c86787357d1965a7ee5efc","tid":191111,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"一份公司做d電氣產品<br />\n係第一次做呢間公司<br />\n係做d對鬼佬客同對大陸廠<br />\n跟只係technical野<br />\n間唔中坐飛機去浙江d廠<br />\n有機會去歐洲同美國出差<br />\n<br />\n第二份<br />\n呢間公司係第二次返去<br />\n第一次走因為唔like上司<br />\n但宜家過左咁耐，好似又冇野了<br />\n公司做電子零件<br />\n做Sales, 要成日出差，要去歐洲，東南亞及印度等<br />\n要meet target, 但老實講target meet唔meet到都係咁<br />\n<br />\n你係我揀邊份工，人工一樣"},{"pid":"87211d0a4810c5a0964c9508da11036b02b7ed53","tid":191111,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"就咁睇,兩份工差唔多<br />\n如果你真係唔再嬲舊上司就返舊公司啦<br />\n起碼熟環境"},{"pid":"2c9cb83482b32a89dd70c23d70fc7e0f28c77de1","tid":191111,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇,兩份工差唔多<br />\n如果你真係唔再嬲舊上司就返舊公司啦<br />\n起碼熟環境</blockquote><br />\n我都諗過<br />\n但新公司同老板同同事初步認識過<br />\n覺得唔錯<br />\n老板係鬼佬，傾過計都幾好<br />\n同埋返呢間公司free d<br />\n<br />\n舊公司就少少formal d , 要著裇衫西褲"},{"pid":"cf71ed14a43d102a838e3b3de4df057cf44faffd","tid":191111,"uid":14695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"新公司<br />\n識下人"},{"pid":"f868df3bb36772ebe7b285f1970e0bc05504fb18","tid":191111,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新公司<br />\n識下人</blockquote><br />\n我都覺新公司好d<br />\n同埋返舊公司做sales, 要搵新客<br />\n其實我麻麻地鐘意呢類duty...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c89798ac0760618c582ab67c79fbf1baf973581","tid":191111,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"其他巴打有冇咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386e00658285e316fa93592cb4295c59a739e17a","tid":191111,"uid":5791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:41:46.000Z","msg":"答案係我兩份都唔揀，呢條好明顯係腦筋急轉彎，你有兩份工關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3186f63b18a88f518381ae926327bdd8f6f1dd21","tid":191111,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>答案係我兩份都唔揀，呢條好明顯係腦筋急轉彎，你有兩份工關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92c7ef3c275022969bd05f18e4a0f664cc13494","tid":191111,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"緊係新公司<br />\n<br />\n返舊公司食回頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你無野唔代表個上司無野"},{"pid":"ef0c9e42b8af577f814a5d26011b88fdca019ba6","tid":191111,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊係新公司<br />\n<br />\n返舊公司食回頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你無野唔代表個上司無野</blockquote><br />\n咁又係<br />\n同舊上司都有出黎食下飯<br />\n都有講有笑<br />\n但都驚驚地之後唔知又咩事"},{"pid":"31706c0183bf148ff317406724e24255c1f45b09","tid":191111,"uid":56976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"新公司，轉下環境"},{"pid":"42f12f465829a217bcf1a4242af9db936ca0e855","tid":191111,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新公司，轉下環境</blockquote><br />\n好，多謝意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725d64f25ad11dfb269a0f3127211cecef92beff","tid":191111,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T23:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472bfe0f7a7fd16c90c769e1003c